title: Match of the Day 01-Feb-2014 720p 50fps HDTV  x264-wAm
description:
Gary Lineker introduces highlights of seven Premier League fixtures, including the 151st Tyne-Wear derby between Newcastle and Sunderland at St James' Park. The Black Cats, who have won their last two games against their old rivals, are looking to complete a league double over the Magpies for the first time since the 1996/97 season. Manchester United travel to the Britannia Stadium to play Stoke, a side they had beaten in 10 of 11 previous Premier League encounters. West Ham's game with Swansea and Cardiff City's meeting with Norwich have implications for teams involved at the wrong end of the table. The day's other games see Everton meet Aston Villa, Fulham play Southampton and Hull entertain Tottenham.


Notes:
Captured and encoded at 50fps to give much smoother movement.
